inn1.comm: slight away movement from just back of a length, Rohit pushes to covers from the crease
shot, little width, very little width, but Rohit waits on the crease, gets on top of the bounce and slaps it past point with superb timing
starts too far outside off and moves further away
straight, good length outside off, nice carry, left alone

an edge past the slips, and it beats third man's dive as well, Rohit plays a length delivery from the crease, slight away movement takes the edge, it is played with soft hands, and does not carry, but this outfield is fast, as usual
left alone outside off

runout chance missed, Holder starts with a full toss just outside off, but Dhawan can't find any timing as the bat closes in his hands, they then decide to go late for a run as mid off converges on the ball, Dhawan would have been gone by more than a couple of feet had that hit, but it's missed by a large margin
straightens outside off, but starts too far outside
some bounce as he bowls it closer to off, left alone
pitched up full, but again too far outside off
hits the pitch back of a length, straightens and bounces, is left alone, then starts to curve in to the keeper
fuller, but still a touch wide, Rohit takes a step out and shoulders arms
nice line, good length right on off stump, Dhawan runs it softly towards point, no chance of a run
pitched up outside off now, close to the stumps, Dhawan lets it go after a step forward
swing for Rampaul as he pitches it up, but it starts on leg and moves down, requiring a one-handed diving take from Charles
length ball on off, softly pushed in front of extra cover for a quick single
bit of away swing again, but the line is a touch wide for the right-hander, left alone
this time he reaches for it outside off and is beaten, Rampaul pitched it up, it left Rohit late as pushed forward
straighter one with some bounce on off, defended
Holder raises both arms in a big appeal for lbw, but this pitched way outside leg as Dhawan missed the flick
now the keeper goes up for caught behind, but there is nothing on this length delivery as it swings down leg
better line now, pitches it up on off, Dhawan forward to push to mid off
dispatched, Holder overpitches it on off stump, and Dhawan leans into the extra-cover drive, reaches 1000 runs for the year as well
slanted further outside off stump, and left alone
even more angle on this one, and it is a wide this time
a slightly slower dipping full delivery now clipped straight to midwicket
good length on the stumps, defended to the leg side
thought about, it, but then pulled the bat away late as this length delivery went past close to off
a helpful full toss on the pad, and Rohit turns it softly in the gap at midwicket, Narine escorts it into the boundary
good length, comes in from outside off now, left alone
goes across to a length ball and pushes from the crease to covers

early breakthrough for West Indies, Rampaul angles it away initially, Rohit sets himself up for the cut, the ball straightens, there is not as much width now, but Rohit still goes hard for the cut, and edges it low to second slip, where the safe hands of Sammy clasp around it
moves away and bounces, but starts way outside off
angles it in to off stump from wider of the crease, Kohli solid in defence
overpitched on the pad, but Dhawan cannot time it well enough to beat mid on to his left
leans forward into a tight defensive push to cover
widish, and comes in with some bounce, left alone
big forward stride to smother a pitched up delivery just outside off
short ball now, outside off, Kohli is surprised by the lift and awkwardly brings it down
full and wide, Kohli goes after it and drills it in the air, but there is deep point
tight line close to off stump, defended
gets some width and punches it hard through the covers, but the sweeper has it covered
lovely, Rampaul overpitches, Dhawan sends it dead straight down the ground with a firm push, no foot, all timing
shortish, swat-pulled down to deep square leg
comes in a tad, Kohli moves across and tickles it behind square, there is no one there, and some chasing is needed
bends the legs and drills this length delivery past short extra cover, the sweeper has some running to do
more runs, Dhawan leans into another drive to an overpitched ball around off, but he's not got much on it, and mid off runs across to field after it passes extra cover
beaten, Dhawan left prodding from the crease as this pitches good length and moves across him
good length on the pad, but Dhawan mistimes the clip and it rolls to square leg
shortish, on the pads again, Dhawan pulls hard but deep square leg cuts it off to his left
comes forward and works a length ball with the incoming angle to midwicket
no width with the changed angle, Dhawan comes forward and defends a length ball, hit close to the splice with some extra bounce
cuts in from back of a length, nudged square on the leg side
slanted across the left-hander on a good length, left alone
pushes forward and runs this pitched up delivery to point
leading edge to extra cover along the ground, Dhawan was trying to work the length ball to the leg side, but played early
slower one, Kohli leans forward calmly and smothers it
slower one overpitched some way outside off, but Kohli picks it from there and turns it through midwicket
overpitches outside off and is drilled off the front foot to the sweeper
walks out and defends to the off side, non-striker wants the single but is rightly sent back
walks across to another overpitched delivery and dismisses it between extra cover and mid off
still full, wider this time, Dhawan flays it straight to extra cover
not exactly on top of the pull but goes through with the stroke, for a single to deep square leg
nudges a length delivery from off stump square on the leg side
another overpitched ball on off clipped down to wide long on
pitches it up, Dhawan's bat-face closes in his hands and he mistimes a drive to mid on
just outside off stump, sent down to third man for one
pitched up delivery driven to wide long on
thick edge races fine to the third man boundary, there is no slip as Dhawan goes for a drive
right on middle and off, Dhawan pushes it down the pitch, Bravo moves across quickly and stops it
flattish delivery straightens on off, punched through extra cover
punched with the turn down to long on
angled in full to the pad, worked through midwicket, deep fielder keeps them to one
reaches for a flighted, wide, full one and drives it past point, who has a chase on his hands
flashes at an overpitched ball and underedges it down the track
puts the front foot across, eyeing the leg side, but cannot work it past midwicket
drilled down the ground but long on cuts it off to his left
walks out and eases a full delivery to the sweeper
slower one outside off, Kohli is right forward to defend
pushes hard at this length delivery and sets off for a single to cover, the throw is way off target but Sammy is backing up superbly with a dive
very wide outside off, slapped away hard and straight to the sweeper
overpitched on middle and leg, he works it softly straight to midwicket
flat and fired down the leg side from over the stumps
tossed up delivery, Dhawan is ready with a lunge and a drive, which beats extra cover, that's all that is required

he's been given, there was sharp and quick turn from outside off, Dhawan was hit on the inside of the front pad in front of middle as he looked to work it to leg, the ball popped up to be caught by a diving Dwayne Bravo at slip, apparently he's been given caught, so umpire Kulkarni thinks there was an inside edge as well, the bowler was already appealing for leg before
on the front foot to defend safely
defends with an open face square on the off side
sharp turn again, from wide outside off, Yuvraj lets it go late
moves across, allows it to spin in and hit the defensive bat hard
reaches for an overpitched and pushes it wide of mid off
angled in, worked out to deep square leg
full on the stumps, defended back to the bowler
drives solidly down to mid off
slanted across, Yuvraj lets it go past
opens the face as he pushes but cannot beat extra cover
full delivery driven to extra cover
flat delivery staying a touch low cut to the sweeper
defended off the front foot to the off side
driven hard but long off is wide and gets to it
leans forward and opens the face to defend towards point
mistimes a swat off a full delivery past square leg for a couple
deep midwicket is vacant, and Kohli slog-sweeps Narine powerfully into the region, picking this from outside off
goes back and works the offbreak with the spin to square leg
sharp turn from outside leg, takes the outside edge and rolls away to the off side as Yiuvraj pushes softly
flighted and overpitched, Yuvraj is able to drive to long off
Kohli moves across for a soft paddle down the leg side, completely in control against the offspinner
spinning into the pad from outside off, Yuvraj leans out and works it to square leg
fuller, similar line, turned to square leg
goes for a big sweep, misses, there is a shout for lbw, but he's hit outside the line of off stump
he sweeps again, this was overpitched, and he almost missed again, but connected just in time, manages decent connection though, needs some footwork from deep square leg to save the boundary
spinning down leg, Yuvraj misses the nudge, there is a hopeful appeal from the keeper for caught behind
tries another sweep, misses again and is hit outside the line again
Yuvraj is missing nearly everything, now he lunges forward to defend, but the ball sneaks through to hit him
walks across and tucks with the spin to square leg, Sammy makes a diving stop, there is some hesitation from Kohli, but Yuvraj is sure he wants to take the single, and does it very safely
spinning across from outside leg, Yuvraj works it behind square leg, and comes back for the second, makes it in time as the throw arrives
beaten, pushes forward inside the line of the offbreak, which pitches leg and ends up outside off
holds bat close to the body as this one spins wide outside off
gets bat to ball now on the forward defensive as this offbreak is pitched up
Narine releases the pressure by dropping it short, and Yuvraj breaks free for the moment by pulling it high over midwicket
tries to cut a full delivery, hits it straight to point
thought of coming down the crease, but stayed in the crease and steered it to short third for one
flat one spinning in down the leg side
succeeds on the sweep this time, takes it from outside off and sends it to the deep square leg rope
hangs back, comes across to a tossed up ball and runs it behind point
goes for a weak drive at a wide ball and is beaten
moves across to a pitched up delivery and defends
spins down the leg side and is called a wide, that actually thudded into the pad, Kohli smiles
the other one that spins away, full outside off, Kohli goes hard at it, and is beaten
almost sneaked through, Kohli is able to get some bat on the paddle just in time else this full ball was hitting leg stump
full delivery worked to square leg
pitches around off and spin away sharply, left alone
overpitched with a bit of flight, smothered safely off the front foot
again he thinks of stepping out but stays there and flashes hard, straight to point
walks out this time and eases it to long off
starts wide outside off and is padded away after it pitched and turns in
Yuvraj jumps out now, Permaul angles it in full, but Yuvraj is able to get bat down and work it to long on
skips out and turns one to wide long on
defends a length ball turning in from outside off, slightly squared up
the straighter one, but was angled in too much, too full and Kohli safely smothers it back
worked behind square leg, beats Sammy's dive from short fine, but there is another man behind him to cut it off
quicker straighter one on Yuvraj;s pads, played out to leg
starts full outside leg stump and turns across, defended tightly off the front foot
big turn across Yuvraj who jabs it away from the crease
overpitched on middle and leg, smothered off the front foot
bit of flight on this one around off, Kohli blocks
more flight, Kohli takes it on the full with a step out and pushes it to the sweeper
nudged off the pad to fine leg
presses forward as if he is going to charge, but stays back and steers to short third
swats a quick and flat one down to wide long on
comes down the track, the ball spins in, hits the front pad and pops away
easily worked square on leg off the pad
straighter one on the stumps, but Yuvraj has a big stride forward and defends safely
offbreak now, Yuvraj is right forward again
beaten this time, this is slightly shorter and jags across Yuvraj, who is half forward
breaks the pressure with a massive blow of a slog-sweep high over deep midwicket, it was the carrom ball
beaten on the cut with a quick one outside off
touch slower, but he is beaten on the cut again
another sweep, Yuvraj is down to pick it as it spins in from outside off, beats deep backward square comfortably
Permaul cracks and bowls it shortish, Yuvraj pulls hard but Holder somehow manages to stop it at deep square leg
pushed to long on for a single
comes in from outside off and strikes Kohli on the pad as the batsman tries to work it to leg
overpitched, the drive finds extra cover
no point, and Kohli drops it softly towards cover for a single
overpitched, outside off, but Yuvraj's drive also races straight to mid off
good length ball into the pads tucked to midwicket for one
the drive is in the air for a while, mid off fields to his left
Kohli reaches one more fifty with a late dab to a length ball that easily beats third man
fine leg is also up, this ball is onto the pad, and Kohli works it past the fielder
into the pad again, worked through square leg now
Yuvraj has tried to conjure a boundary here and has given it away, this ball was just back of good length, not short at all, he's tried to pick and pull it over midwicket, but found the man tamely
reaches for a wide delivery and thick-edges down to third man past wide slip
good length ball on off stump, picked away to deep square leg
walks out to a short of a length ball, finds midwicket with the tuck
overpitched ball pushed down to long on
shortish ball to Raina, but it does not get up much and is tucked off the hip to deep square leg
straightens outside off stump from back of a length, steered to point
opens the face to a good length ball and finds point again
pitched up now, Kohli tries to work it to leg but ends up pushing back to the bowler
walks across looking to nudge to the leg side but misses quite awkwardly
walks down the pitch now and gets the single to long on
has a mighty swing at this full delivery but cannot beat cover
hit down to long on for one
punches a good length ball against the turn to point
swats this shortish ball with the turn down to deep backward square
good length ball slapped to sweeper cover
starts with a cutter on the pads and is tickled for four past the keeper's dive
on the pad again, good length this time, worked to deep square leg
opens the face from the crease and runs it down to third man
dropped, captain puts down Kohli, it was a offcutter, Kohli popped it back trying to work it to leg, it was dying on Bravo, he went low to his left, it hit his hand and rolled away
length ball pushed to the sweeper
Bravo escapes, he bowls it full and quick on the pads, Kohli flicks it in the air but straight to to fine leg
half tracker, picked from outside off and banished to the deep midwicket boundary
now wide outside off, Kohli accepts the second gift and cuts it to the deep point rope
gets it on target this time, good length straightening on the pad, nudged square
another poor ball, short and spinning into the pad, but Raina finds fine leg
eased past point, who makes an absolute mess of it and ends up escorting to close to the sweeper, but only a single conceded
on the pads again, Raina is not missing out this time, he flicks it away for four more
good length ball worked to deep midwicket
thick outside edge in the air for a while, down to a third man
poor line once more from Bravo, half a foot down the pad, and Kohli accepts one more gift with a fine tickle
walks out and pushes a length ball to mid off
closes the face and taps a short ball through square leg
wide ball to Raina, who reaches forward and pings sweeper cover for a single

another catch dropped, Powell puts down an absolute sitter at short fine leg, not that the ball deserved a wicket, it was a half tracker down the leg side, Raina swatted it straight to Powell, into his hands and out
thick inside edge past the keeper
good length ball punched down to wide long off
pitched up to off and middle, pushed to long on
slower one loops in full and is defended back to the bowler
Raina steers this length ball but short third man scrambled to his right to stop it
backs away outside leg, bowler follows him from round the wicket, Raina's push finds point
Raina takes a step outside leg stump and picks this full delivery over the bowler
controls a short ball reasonably well and takes a single to backward square leg
pitched up delivery driven, straight to midwicket
short and slow, Kohli waits and swats it just past Samuels at midwicket
comes across and pushes for a single to long on
loopy full toss on the pad, Kohli pushes it in the gap at midwicket to come back for two
Holder gets it in the blockhole, jammed down the ground for a single
shortish from round the stumps to Raina, who nudges it to short fine leg
pitched full, pushed hard to long on
Raina's drive off this overpitched, widish ball finds extra cover
Holder sends in another one around the blockhole, outside off, and Raina cannot do much with it
straighter one punched down the ground to bring up the 200
spinning across the left-hander, who dabs it to short third man
straighter one jagging across Kohli, pushed to point
offbreak straightening on off now, worked to midwicket
nudged square on the leg side
spins away from off stump, left alone
length ball on the pad turned in front of square leg
Raina falls by the swipe, Rampaul pitches it up from round the wicket, angles it in to leg stump, Raina swings, and top-edges to extra cover
opens the face but his steer finds short third man
a slower one, Kohli knocks it back, Rampaul's dive cannot prevent the single
comes across and defends a length ball
Dhoni gets a short ball, and pulls it on one leg, down to fine leg
carrom ball spinning away outside off, Dhoni cuts and point half-stops it
worked off the pad to deep square leg
straighter one turning onto the pad, Dhoni cannot beat square leg
moves across and pushes an offspinner to mid on
tossed up full, blocked to midwicket
angles an offbreak across Dhoni, who punches it back
moves to 99 with a push to midwicket and a quick single
Kohli was charging for the single, but Dhoni sent him back after awkwardly squirting a full delivery to extra cover
accurate stuff from Rampaul, good length on off stump, punched to covers
length on middle now, Dhoni calmly plays it out to extra cover
pushes in the air, Sammy fields to his left at mid off

Kohli is out for 99, it was a bouncer at the head, Kohli pulled, the ball swirled down to fine leg, where the giant Holder dives forward to pluck it very low, then gets up and roars as Kohli stands stunned, they check for the no-ball but Rampaul is alright
nudged to midwicket off the front foot
full ball played out to midwicket
full and angled in, pushed back
offbreak, Dhoni goes back and punches, finds extra cover
huge turn from outside off, hits Dhoni on the thigh pad
lovely, the carrom ball now, Dhoni plays inside the line as it spins away a shade, beaten
shortish and wide, cut to deep point
length ball bounces and hits the bat high as Dhoni shuffles and tickles it square on the leg side
super effort from captain Bravo at a shortish backward point, Jadeja had timed the steer quite well
and out of nowhere, Dhoni decides it is time to break his drought, a step forward and boom, the length ball flies high over long off
keeps strikes with a single through covers
played to square leg
lunges forward and turns this full delivery behind square
reaches forward to defend a pitched up offbreak
shortish offbreak cut hard, to sweeper cover
straighter one kicks on off stump, Dhoni goes deep in the crease and keeps it down
another carrom ball, Dhoni is right back and keeps strike again with a single to point
a low full toss on the pad but Dhoni flicks it straight to square leg
rolls away to the leg side off the pad as Dhoni misses the length delivery
straightens on off stump, Jadeja softly plays it behind point
steers a short and wide ball to third man, where Rampaul messes up and concedes another run
another low full toss finds the field, Jadeja drives straight to extra cover
slow cutter comes in from outside leg stump, Jadeja nudges it for a single
lunges forward to defend a full ball to the off side
the carrom ball, Jadeja did not pick it, was trying to steer expecting turn away from him, got hit on the gloves as it kicked in
big offbreak now beating the forward defensive
into the pad but Jadeja cannot get it away
chops this quick delivery to second slip, a second slip in the 45th over
Narine ends with another maiden, both of them coming after the 40th over
Dhoni jabs a full one square and sprints, Narine throws from square leg and smacks Dhoni on the right glove, immediately apologises, Dhoni holds a hand up signalling all is fine
he was expecting this to go down leg and shouldered arms, but it hit him on the pad
slower one, nudged in front of square leg, and they manage to take two by the time someone gets to the ball
slams a full delivery to cover, throw misses at the striker's. Dhoni would have been in anyway
Dhoni swings hard but cannot get much on this low full toss, takes two to deep midwicket
poor end to the over from Bravo, and Dhoni latches on immediately, full toss down the pad, Dhoni swings it flat over the deep backward square leg boundary
Jadeja backs away and has a swing, a thick edge runs fine, but third man is pretty fine too and runs around
nice, a slow length ball on off stump, Dhoni pushes it and will get only one down the ground

that'll do, Jadeja has looked thoroughly unconvincing, and has his leg stump uprooted, he just stands in the crease and wafts weakly, Rampaul angles the length ball in, past whatever Jadeja was trying, and into the stumps
a leading edge as Ashwin is hurried by Rampaul's pace on this length ball, which scurries past cover
that rolls into the deep point boundary, should have been stopped really, wasn't too far from Permaul at point, as Dhoni played that stabbing square drive
Dhoni creates another boundary, he comes across and helps a shortish ball comfortably wide of short fine leg
Ashwin was plumb lbw had he missed this full delivery, but he manages a feather on it to send it fine down the leg side
Ashwin picks this shortish ball and pulls it straight to the man at deep midwicket, played quite nonchalantly, but picked the fielder
another poor effort in the field from Darren Bravo at wide long on, Dhoni picks a low full toss over midwicket, Bravo had it covered with a run to his right, but it rolls under him
full delivery, Dhoni works it to deep midwicket
Ashwin has a slog, doesn't middle it and the ball rolls to deep midwicket
right in the blockhole from Holder, Dhoni jams it through midwicket, he charges for the first, he wants the second, but by then, long on has reached the ball
Dhoni has a swing and misses a back of a length ball that comes a touch slowly off the pitch
connects this time and swings a short of a length ball to deep square leg
Ashwin bends the knee and has a slog, but it is a slower one and he is beaten outside off
now he makes room outside leg, Rampaul pitches it up, Ashwin drills it straight to extra cover
Dhoni spoils Rampaul's tight over, he gets a delivery pitched up just outside off stump, and sends it high over long on

50th ODI fifty for the India captain, he was on 3 off 17, Rampaul tries it full again, this time on the stumps, but Dhoni is able to get under it, a mix of a stab and a swing gives him six more, over deep midwicket
now Ashwin backs away and lofts cleanly over extra cover
slogs a full ball in front of square leg, there are two to be taken, but Dhoni wants the strike
he's got away with this, a high full toss, Dhoni gives it all but only manages a single to deep midwicket
a slower one, Ashwin has a huge swing at it, it seems to have gone straight up but eventually lands beyond the deep square leg rope
he tries a reverse sweep, against a fast bowler, goes down on a knee outside leg stump, but only feathers it through to the keeper
Holder keeps it full around off final ball and India will get only a single to point

inn2.comm: a straightening length ball dabbed past the couple of slips to third man
almost played on, Powell pushes forward to defend, Bhuvneshwar gets it to swing in late into the left-hander, and Powell chops it close to off stump
length ball slanted across, left alone
slips it wider across the left-hander, who lets it go
overpitched delivery driven with an open face, Rohit at cover dives full-length to save a certain boundary
no stopping it this time, Charles punches  a length ball between extra cover and mid off, from where Dhawan gives chase but this outfield is too quick for him
length ball moving away widish outside off, cut away to square third man
pushes at a skiddy length delivery, outside edge zooms past the two slips, and beats third man's dive
width on the 137 kph length ball but Charles swats it to cover
the ball is flying down to third man on the bounce as Charles flashes at a rising length ball
good length on middle and leg, turned to midwicket, still quite new both the balls, but they seem to be coming on better than the earlier pair did in the afternoon
pitched up at 134.8 kph, on the stumps, pushed back to the bowler
squeezed through the gap at cover for a couple of runs
width outside off, Charles drives, straight to cover
plays out a good length ball to point

Bhuvneshwar finds himself in the way of this mistimed swat from Charles, it smacks him in the stomach, he wraps his hands around the ball and sends Charles back, Charles went after this length ball, but it bounced and hit the bat quite high, so that it looped back and took Bhuvneshwar down as well, he's lost his breath but the wicket will help him get it back
this stays low now, but was safely outside off stump, what is with Samuels and rollers?
tentatively pushes a length ball down the track
flowing punch from the crease to point off a good length ball
walks down the pitch and punches to mid off, there was a chance of a run out, had Shami picked the ball up cleanly, but it slipped through his hands
stays a shade low this length ball as Samuels punches from the crease to mid off
Samuels now flows into a smooth drive but cover dives and saves runs, a boundary probably
Samuels goes after this wide ball, there is a thick inside edge, but it hits ground just before it enters Dhoni's gloves
135 kph pitched up delivery, Samuels takes a hand off the bat handle as he checks the drive back to the bowler
rising on the pads, tucked away, square leg cuts off the single
they are hitting the ball to the field regularly West Indies, another drive now, hits the ground hard and bounces to cover
there again, clipped neatly off the pad but straight to square leg
driven with nice timing but cannot beat the off-side field
all the field-finding makes him rush for a single after tucking one wide of mid on, he is sent back after speeding half way down the track, but the throw is as wild as they come
loud shout for leg-before as he misses the flick but that pitched outside leg, umpire Kulkarni stays unmoved
Samuels drives a length delivery, finds extra cover, ho hum, at the moment, there are no gaps
now Samuels picks the gap, a touch overpitched and wide from Mohit, Samuels splits the opening between extra cover and mid off
similar line and length from Mohit, Samuels goes in the air now, again between extra cover and mid off with an open face, four more

this is sensational from Dhoni, Mohit is bowling well into the mid-130s, the captain decides to come up, the bowler gets one to move in slightly after pitching on a good length, Samuels goes for another drive, and the thin edge is snapped up low by the captain, who jumps immediately in delight, what a sharp, sharp take
moves forward outside off to block, inside edge onto pad
overpitched, Bravo times the drive, but his open face sends it straight into point's hands
edged, but slip is too wide and Powell will get four, this length delivery rose, Powell tried to punch from the crease, and escaped
Bhuvneshwar tries the short ball, Powell pulls it from around chest height, in the air, to the deep backward square rope
pushes a pitched up delivery with a closed face to mid on
good length ball punched to cover
overpitched at 135.8 kph from Bhuvneshwar, Powell sends it straight down the ground with a firm push
full delivery driven straight to mid on
bounce from back of a length as this comes in, left alone
worked off the pad to fine leg
Powell hits the big gap at extra cover off this full delivery and picks up a boundary
he went for the cover drive again, but this one moved in a bit with the angle, and he is beaten
drives an overpitched delivery but there is a wide long off in place
good length outside off, eased to point
closer to off stump, good length, jabbed down to third man
finds some extra bounce on off stump, is defended towards point
is cramped for room with this length ball on middle and leg, and cannot work it away far from the bowler
goes across and defends this one on off stump
now Bravo finds the gap at extra cover on this length delivery, it is a big one, and there is no stopping this boundary
tries to drive a pitched up ball outside off but mistimes it completely
walks out, gets to the pitch of this one and eases it past the bowler to long off
Bravo gets some room outside off and scythes this overpitched ball past cover, gave it everything
lovely, there is not much of an opening between the two men at cover, but Bravo splits it with a another stinging drive, Mohit overpitching again
and another one, opens the face and goes hard at a length ball, it flies in the air over point
drops this length ball softly in front of point and keep strike
tossed up from round the stumps, in the air for a while as it is pushed to extra cover
angled in full on middle, pushed softly to the off side
sharp turn outside off now, Bravo beaten as he prods forward
this hurries on towards off stump now, Bravo goes back to keep it out
overpitched flighted ball driven straight to short cover
Bravo plays with an open face, but softly, and this does not carry to slip
flat one sits up outside off, is slapped down to long off
tucked off the pad to midwicket
plays a pitched up ball off the back foot, it rushes on and is played out to midwicket
comes down the track, Raina darts it in to the legs, but Powell adjusts superbly to clip it past midwicket
goes deep in the crease to push to the off side
moves out of the crease again and keeps strike with a push to long on
angled in to off from wide of the crease, blocked
turn from off stump, punched off the back foot to point for a quick single
tossed up high and into middle, driven to short cover
flatter and quicker, cut away to the sweeper
skips out and nudges a single to deep backward square leg
tossed up very full on middle stump, he slams a drive down to long off
quick and full into middle and off, Bravo is a tad slow in getting low to defend and gets an inside edge onto pad
hit off the back foot to the sweeper
charges out after pushing in front of extra cover, but is sent back as Jadeja converges on the ball
works a full delivery to mid on for a single
does not time this drive but it still beats point to his left
quick and flat into the pads, and Bravo has got enough of a tickle on it
closes the face as he pushes this tossed up ball down the track, Ashwin finds Bravo in the way and the single is on to long on
length ball straightening on off stump, defended
tries to push a tossed up ball to covers, it takes a thick inside edge and goes towards mid on
tries to cut a pitched up delivery close to off stump and is beaten
flicks a full delivery to midwicket
hurries on towards off stump before Bravo punches it away to covers
driven down to the man at long off
thick inside edge to deep square leg as he tries a big drive
slanted in to the pad, stays low, is picked away in front of square leg
gives it some flight, it is defended off the front foot
full, worked down to long on for one
another single to long on to a full delivery
gives it a lot of air, Bravo goes after it, and lofts it in the air over cover, to the sweeper
eased down to long on
pierces the offside infield with a drive along the ground, sweeper fields
angled in, knocked to midwicket
shortens it as he sees the batsman coming out, it's pushed back tamely to him
squirts this full delivery with the spin to long off
punches a pitched up ball off the back foot to sweeper cover
pushed towards point
there is sweeper cover, there is wide long off, but Bravo leans into another cover drive and hits it right between those two men
goes back and cuts it away to sweeper cover
full one pushed to the off side
nudged to square leg off the pad
makes him drive a flighted ball, to extra cover
refuses to drive this tossed up ball now, plays it softly and runs it to slip
quicker and angled in to middle, defended back
flashes late at this full delivery outside off and it runs off a thick edge past slip
tossed up ball on off stump, defended off the front foot
tosses it up much wider now, Bravo lets it go
Shami starts with one full on the pads, and it runs away fine into the boundary
better line, hits the bat hard from a good length as he defends
opens the face on this rising delivery and eases it behind point, but the fielder prevents the single
moves across and picks this full delivery off middle and leg
sharp stop from Shami in his followthrough, bends low to his left and plucks out a drive to throw it back at the striker's end
a bouncer now on the stumps, Powell ducks
backs away and cuts to the man at sweeper cover
Ashwin shortens it a tad as he sees Powell coming out, it hits the pad and rolls away on the off side
stays in the crease now, allows it to come on and tickles it behind square leg
dropped, Dhoni's put down a straightforward chance, Bravo wafted at this tossed up ball that spun away from him, thin edge without any deviation hit Dhoni's gloves and popped out
defended calmly off the front foot now
dropped,/b> again, much tougher chance this time, Bravo flashes hard and a thick edge flies to slip, where Raina parries it away behind him, came in at head high, very tough one
all happening, and India have missed their third chance in four balls, Bravo pushes this length ball back at Shami, it hurries to his left, bowler stretches out a hand but it is too late
a thick outside edge runs past the keeper along the ground to the third man boundary as Shami bowls it very full close to off stump, Bravo squeezed his bat down on it
fifty for Darren Bravo, off another thick edge, he's squared up this time by a sharp length ball which scoots to point

picks this full delivery straight over the bowler, hasn't timed it as well as his followthrough looks, it plops into the outfield, Yuvraj at mid on thought it was going to run into the rope, and started chasing it late, but managed to drag it back with a slide in the end
bangs it in shortish and down the leg side now
shorter goes Shami and Powell plays a powerful pull, smacking it into the crowd over deep midwicket

the partnership is broken on 100, this time Dhoni holds on to the catch, Bravo tries to cut one too close to the off stump, and it is a healthy edge to the keeper, once again, West Indies have given India an opening, despite the numerous dropped catches, just reward for Ashwin, who has bowled with superb control with a wet ball
good length ball spins sharply down the leg side
defended off the front foot
whipped with the spin through square leg
eases into a front-foot push to sweeper cover
tossed up from round the stumps, he squirts it behind point for one
full into the pad, and tickled fine, it will beat a sprinting fine leg, and bring up Powell's half-century
punches a length ball to the off side
good length ball angled in, whipped off the pad
sweeps from way outside off stump to deep square leg
comes in with the angle to off stump, is punched to long off
full one pushed back to the bowler
nudged to midwicket with the spin
pushes a flighted ball to long off
quicker length delivery hurries in, is punched to point
takes it from middle and nudges it behind square leg
punched off the back foot to extra cover
tosses it quite high, it ends up as a full toss on the pad, and is put away to deep square leg
full on the stump, he is forward to block
big turn for Jadeja outside off as Simmons is beaten on the drive
an outside edge now as Jadeja finds more turn, but it does not carry to slip
defended off the front foot
Simmons winds up and slogs, gets it over mid on
left alone outside off stump
lovely drive, reached out and drilled it past point,  but the sweeper will get to it

oh dear, what's Powell done, he's walked out in a daze past Ashwin's flighted offbreak, big turn past the bat as he tries to weakly defend, stranded miles down the track, another waste of a wicket, more reward for the disciplined Ashwin
technically a chance as a thick inside edge balloons past short leg
clips a full and flighted ball down to long on
thick outside edge runs past the lone slip
gets forward to defend down the track
flat delivery outside off cut behind point, past the fielder';s dive and will run away into the rope
more width, another cut, this one is well wide of point and he has no chance
straightens on off stump, defended off the back foot
pushed back to the bowler
very full on the stumps, can;t beat the bowler with a push
pushed off the front foot to point for a single
the drier balls are gripping and bouncing now, this one turns in past the defensive prod, takes the pad flap and flies down the leg side
worked to square leg off the back foot
Yuvraj dives at point to stop this drive and save some runs
pushes forward to smother this offbreak
Ashwin tries a different action and hurls this in full, a surprised Bravo stabs it square on the leg side
tossed up ball blocked off the front foot
pushed back to the bowler from middle
opens the face and runs it behind point
short, too short, but Bravo can only slap it to short extra cover
dabs it behind point for a quick single
drills a drive off a full delivery to point
tight over from Raina, his dive fails to stop this push, but midwicket running across does
jabs this full delivery through cover for a single
length ball played out to point quietly
paddles from off stump and connects well enough to beat a squarish fine leg
thick inside edge as this comes in with the angle, scurries behind square leg
knocks it off the pad straight to midwicket
tosses it up full, Bravo drives it back
worked straight to midwicket
cannot get it away again, punches to the bowler now
right on middle stump, punched down to long off
a full ball on off stump, Bravo cannot get it past the bowler
a straighter delivery now, Bravo drives expecting turn, and is beaten
Bravo gets something out of the over with his flourish of a lofted drive over extra cover, just clearing the leap from the man in the ring
opens the face and defends off the front foot to cover
short, and cut very hard, but Yuvraj has thrown himself to his left at backward point and saved a certain boundary
dropped into the leg side softly, they advance for a single, but Jadeja prevents it
some bounce now from a good length, defended off the front foot, hits the bat high
drives a full delivery to long on
his push finds extra cover, and that will be drinks
whips a length ball off middle and leg to deep midwicket
nudges and hesitates, but the ball is clear of square leg and the single is on
flat and quick, slightly short, and Bravo is instantly rocking back and thumping it hard past extra cover
slower this time, into the pad, worked square
Raina runs to his left and dives but cannot stop this push from rolling along to long off
straight and shortish outside off, Bravo waits and cuts, but cannot beat the man at sweeper cover
turns a length delivery on the stumps into the leg side
bounce from back of a length, Bravo goes back, rides it, and plays it down to backward point

and another West Indies gift falls in India's lap, Bravo had batted quite well till now, he's tried manufacturing a boundary with a pick-up pull on one leg, and has found the man on the deep square leg boundary with precision
length ball turned to square leg and Sammy is away
flows into a drive to an overpitched ball, to sweeper cover
stabs a length delivery to backward point for a single
fired into the pad, nudged to short fine
defends to the man at forward short leg
presses forward again and smothers another one
does not turn and hits the pad, Jadeja shouts, but that is going down leg
full into the pad again, pushed to backward square leg

Jadeja will end with a maiden, Sammy squeezes this wide of cover and sets off but he has to turn backs as the fielder comes in, a maiden in the batting Powerplay, to Darren Sammy, nothing Ravindra Jadeja cannot do
punches a short of a length ball off the back foot to mid off
steered to short third man
good length ball punched hard to the sweeper
a low full toss jabbed awkwardly to mid off
stays on the crease and stabs this length ball to point for one
angled in, whipped off the pad to deep square leg
sees the batsman back way to leg and follows him, Simmons then whips it into the leg side for a couple
presses forward to defend a quick delivery angled in
eyes deep midwicket with a slog sweep but cant get the ball off the pitch
comes forward and defends to the off side
drives it down to long off for a single
Sammy brings out a slog, but his connection is not much more than a very weak underedge
punched off the back foot to extra cover for a quick, tight single
length ball tapped towards midwicket for a single
a mistimed drive hurries just out of the bowler's reach for a single to mid off
turns this from outside off stump to deep midwicket
into middle and leg, and whipped wide of deep square leg for an easy couple to bring up the 200
good length ball punched crisply but straight to extra cover
stabs a length ball on off to mid on
slapped away on one leg, in the air but falls short of extra cover
reaches for a pitched up ball and drives, but finds extra cover once more
clipped to midwicket off the pad, Simmons makes it safely as the throw misses
length ball turned to deep midwicket from off stump
a stylish drive finds the fielder at extra cover yet again
beaten outside off stump as he tries to square-drive from the crease
punches hard, beats extra cover, but not long off
no stopping this, a low full toss outside off, Sammy drills it harder past extra cover and long off has to give up early
lovely placement from Sammy, a short of a length ball around off, he takes it from there and turns the wrists to whip it to the deep square leg rope
beaten outside off stump this time, the length delivery bounces in front of Dhoni, not a slower one, clocked at 137.7 kph
Sammy gets two more, reaches out to an overpitched ball and beats Jadeja at point with the drive, the sweeper runs around in the deep

dropped, how many catches have been dropped this match, Yuvraj now at long on, Simmons decided to have a heave and sliced this fullish delivery high, Yuvraj had it covered, but it popped out, he tried again, it popped out again, he had a third go, but it eluded him still and plonked into the turf
pushed to midwicket for a single
mistimes a drive to point, not getting the single
taken from middle and worked to square leg for one

substitute Rayudu lts it r-i-p from midwicket, this is a missile of a throw, Dhoni has no chance to collect, fortunately the backing up is good at short third man, only one overthrow, there is a chance to run out the non-striker, but the throw to the bowler is not strong enough
Sammy is producing a little sensible gem, he now swats the last delivery of the over, a tame short one, into the crowd at deep square leg
Simmons cranks up and deposits Jadeja way over deep midwicket with a powerful slog-sweep, brings up fifty, the third of the innings
tries to work it to the leg side, but bowler is in the way
sharp turn for Jadeja, Simmons was backing away to leg, he has to reach out to dab this to short third man
but Sammy shows superb sense again, this is shortish alright, but he's placed it neatly past backward square leg
hit on the pad, they go up in appeal, but umpire Kulkarni says no, clearly going down leg
a very late decision to let this go outside off stump, he was pushing forward initially
a slower one on off stump, Simmons adjusts and eases it to point for one
Sammy gives it a heave-ho, there is a sound on the replay as the back of a length ball passes the bat, but no one appealed, Dhoni's reaction suggests he thought Sammy just missed it
dabs a widish ball to point for one
a slower one, batsman is backing away and has to adjust to stab it square on the off side, almost took out off stump this one, Simmons got the bat down just in time
this is in Darren Sammy's range, full, into the pad, and he's picked it 94 metres into the crowd over deep midwicket
Mohit sends this length delivery down the leg side now, pressure right on India
a slower one once more, Sammy lunges forward and squeezes it into the off side to keep the strike
Sammy defends towards point, Simmons wants the single, is sent back rightly
another dot, he follows this one outside off and runs it to short third man
into the pad, rolls square, Dhoni cannot stop the single
Jadeja has another lbw appeal, but Simmons has knocked this off a thick inside edge onto his pad flap
Simmons eyes deep midwicket with a huge swing, but only squirts it to square leg for one

Sammy is winding up, he is looking for the big one, but he reins himself in and taps this into the off side, has been the defining feature of his innings, the success in restraining his attacking instincts
that came back in a mile, Simmons was setting himself up for a big stroke when this jagged back in and pinged him on the thigh pad
Simmons has lost his head again, charged Shami for a wild heave, but the top edge has fallen way short of the advancing long off
new bat in hand, Sammy swings, and the full all flies in the gap at midwicket, but long on cuts it off, keeps them to just one
Simmons gets the boundary, he backs away and cuts, Dhawan at sweeper cover spots the ball too late, he went the wrong way initially, and it is too late by the time he recovers
Shami gets one around the blockhole, Simmons is shuffling about in the crease and pushes it down the ground
massive, Darren Sammy gets a full toss and mows it high over long-on, it looked at first he might have a chance, but it cleared him by a fair distance
backs away and cuts hard, finds backward point
Simmons tries the slog sweep, does not connect, is hit on the body, and takes the leg bye
Sammy defends, a thick inside edge rolls to vacant midwicket, and another single is on
Simmons goes a long way outside leg but ends up choppingthe cut, short third man fields to his right
drills a full delivery out to wide long off

that's a goner, with the last ball of his spell, Jadeja keeps India alive, this comes in with the angle, Simmons is caught on the crease, misses the whip and is hit low on the pad in front of middle and leg
a low full toss driven wide of long off, but they'll get only a single, and that brings up a sensible, vital half-century for the West Indies Test captain
that is another chance, albeit a tough one, there is a sound as the ball passes Holder's bat on the attempted drive, but Dhoni is standing up, and this one does no stick
this drive hits the gap between short third man and backward point, and Holder releases a lot of pressure with this boundary
pushed down to long off for a single
Sammy is sealing this for West Indies, a full toss around off stump, he swings it right between deep midwicket and long on
that should do it, Sammy receives another high full toss and smashes it in the same region, this time it clears deep midwicket past the desperate, futile attempt from the fielder
flicked elegantly in the air off the pad and Holder comes back for a couple
Holder gives it away with a skip down the track and a swing of the bat, thick edge settles into Dhoni's gloves, quite needless
on the stumps, pushed back to the bowler
mistimes a drive and the ball rolls to extra cover

oh dear, another one throws it away, Narine tries an almighty pull, he is hurried for pace on the short ball, and the top edge ends in square leg's hands, they cross over, and Sammy will be on strike next ball

Sammy goes for glory off the short ball and swipes hard, it flies in the air, Yuvraj at midwicket puts in a theatrical dive, but it eludes him, there is a man in the deep though, and Sammy keeps strike for the last over
Sammy was winding up, but he saw this bowled slow, and reined himself in to tap it into the off side for a single
Mohit goes up in appeal for lbw, this cut in and hit him too high, Sammy and Permaul kept their cool to sneak in the leg bye as the ball rolls square on the off side

that shall do it for West Indies, Darren Sammy gets under this pitched up delivery and lifts it over the infield, there is deep midwicket, but a single is all West Indies need, and Sammy strolls to the other end with a smile on his face
